game.name: Elsa Closet Challenge
game.description:
This time dressing challenge is going to be more interesting and engaging since it comes with a kind of unique activity where you have to find out the objects too apart from dressing her girl. Do you think that you have the ability to accept this new kind of challenge? Join Elsa Closet Challenge Game and find all the objects she needs before dressing her up! You would have 10 objects and 10 seconds to find them all. 
Remember you do not have time to waste as Elsa wants to join a ball tonight. It will be your responsibility now to help the lady find them all and leave the home with an awesome look in this brand new dress up game. Try to be very fast as you would have only the limited time to complete your goal successfully! There are approximately 10 things, including teacups, tiaras and pearls that are scattered at different places around her bedroom. 
Be careful at the details and find all the objects fast as you will have only 1 minute to complete your first level in this html5 finding games for kids! Your good fashion sense has given Elsa to hire you as her personal stylist, so do not forget to give your fashion advice to the princess so that she can pick up an impressive outfit for the party. Mix and match as many outfits as you can to make the most beautiful Disney princess ever!
